      "updated": 1782265000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MVP orchestration service - TypeScript / NestJS\nOwns event intake, validation, idempotency, state routing, provider clients, retries, technical traceability and report handoff. It does not own portal UI, Odoo UI or clinical/genetic repositories.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MVP orchestration service - TypeScript / NestJS\nOwns event intake, validation, idempotency, state routing, provider clients, retries, technical traceability and report handoff. It does not own portal UI, Odoo UI or clinical/genetic repositories.",
