      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PostgreSQL tecnico\nStores only IDs, event metadata, state snapshots, idempotency keys, retry/error records and sanitized audit markers.\nNo raw genetic data. No documents. No report contents.",
