      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Flow 3 - TellmeGen external/manual\nAitor/equipo uses TellmeGen B2B outside MVP. Test/result milestones are updated manually in Odoo. No TellmeGen data enters PostgreSQL automatically.",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
